{"hash":"gridsome","data":{"post":{"id":"37","title":"Setup Vim Airline (in Termux)","summary":"","body":"\n<p>Vim airline is a tool to enhance the looking of vim. And it is a little tricky to setup especially in termux.</p>\n<p>As I did not install any package manager for vim (in fact, I failed to install and setup Vundle), I need to clone the repo to <code>~/.vim/pack/dist/start/</code> to let vim automatically load the package. And I see the airline when I opened vim.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>By the way, all packages I tested (NERDTree, indentLine, gitgutter) all support this kind of operation.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>\n      <a id=\"article-trouble-shooting\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#trouble-shooting\">\n      #</a> Trouble Shooting</h2>\n<h4>\n      <a id=\"article-only-mode-and-filename-is-displayed\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#only-mode-and-filename-is-displayed\">\n      #</a> Only mode and filename is displayed!</h4>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508103-03622e80-b626-11ea-840e-45b6fd654bc4.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508103-03622e80-b626-11ea-840e-45b6fd654bc4.jpg\" alt=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>For termux disable the auto truncate of section A,B,C and Z is perfect. That is, let other sections truncate at a larger width than your screen.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-viml\">\n      <div class=\"code-bar\">\n      <span class=\"mdi mdi-content-copy\"></span>\n      <span class=\"code-lang\">viml</span>\n      </div><pre><code><span class=\"pl-k\">let</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\"><span class=\"pl-k\">g:</span>airline</span>#extensions#default#section_truncate_width <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-cce\">\\ </span><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>warning<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>: <span class=\"pl-c1\">80</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-cce\">\\ </span><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>error<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>: <span class=\"pl-c1\">80</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-cce\">\\ </span><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>x<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>: <span class=\"pl-c1\">80</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-cce\">\\ </span><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>y<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>: <span class=\"pl-c1\">80</span>}</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Note: Only when nocompatible set can you use <code>\\</code> to continue line.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508112-06f5b580-b626-11ea-95d6-117280dbb331.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508112-06f5b580-b626-11ea-95d6-117280dbb331.jpg\" alt=\"1\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h4>\n      <a id=\"article-no-fancy-gt-s-there\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#no-fancy-gt-s-there\">\n      #</a> No fancy <code>&gt;</code> s there!</h4>\n<p>Enable fancy fonts!</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-viml\">\n      <div class=\"code-bar\">\n      <span class=\"mdi mdi-content-copy\"></span>\n      <span class=\"code-lang\">viml</span>\n      </div><pre><code><span class=\"pl-k\">let</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\"><span class=\"pl-k\">g:</span>airline_powerline_fonts</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">1</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508126-0bba6980-b626-11ea-8090-d453cc5431b7.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508126-0bba6980-b626-11ea-8090-d453cc5431b7.jpg\" alt=\"2\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h4>\n      <a id=\"article-there-are-dots-following-the-mode\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#there-are-dots-following-the-mode\">\n      #</a> There are dots following the mode!</h4>\n<p>Set the name of the modes!</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-viml\">\n      <div class=\"code-bar\">\n      <span class=\"mdi mdi-content-copy\"></span>\n      <span class=\"code-lang\">viml</span>\n      </div><pre><code><span class=\"pl-k\">let</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\"><span class=\"pl-k\">g:</span>airline_mode_map</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-cce\">\\ </span><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>c<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>: <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>C<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-cce\">\\ </span><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>n<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>: <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>N<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-cce\">\\ </span><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>V<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>: <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>V<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-cce\">\\ </span><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>i<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>:<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>I<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>}</code></pre></div>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508140-107f1d80-b626-11ea-81da-ead9b8cba948.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508140-107f1d80-b626-11ea-81da-ead9b8cba948.jpg\" alt=\"3\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h4>\n      <a id=\"article-i-do-not-need-the-section-z-so-long\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#i-do-not-need-the-section-z-so-long\">\n      #</a> I do not need the section Z so long!</h4>\n<p>Set the custom section z!</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-viml\">\n      <div class=\"code-bar\">\n      <span class=\"mdi mdi-content-copy\"></span>\n      <span class=\"code-lang\">viml</span>\n      </div><pre><code><span class=\"pl-k\">let</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\"><span class=\"pl-k\">g:</span>airline_section_z</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>%2l/%L☰%2v<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508160-15dc6800-b626-11ea-9bd9-c61665238640.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508160-15dc6800-b626-11ea-9bd9-c61665238640.jpg\" alt=\"4\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h4>\n      <a id=\"article-what-if-i-need-a-tab-bar\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#what-if-i-need-a-tab-bar\">\n      #</a> What if I need a tab bar?</h4>\n<p>Enable it and set the good style!</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-viml\">\n      <div class=\"code-bar\">\n      <span class=\"mdi mdi-content-copy\"></span>\n      <span class=\"code-lang\">viml</span>\n      </div><pre><code><span class=\"pl-k\">let</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\"><span class=\"pl-k\">g:</span>airline</span>#extensions#<span class=\"pl-c1\">tabline</span>#enabled<span class=\"pl-k\">=</span><span class=\"pl-c1\">1</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">let</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\"><span class=\"pl-k\">g:</span>airline</span>#extensions#<span class=\"pl-c1\">tabline</span>#formatter <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>unique_tail<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508166-183ec200-b626-11ea-8f93-68715729d3f2.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508166-183ec200-b626-11ea-8f93-68715729d3f2.jpg\" alt=\"5\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h4>\n      <a id=\"article-the-word-count-is-annoying\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#the-word-count-is-annoying\">\n      #</a> The word count is annoying!</h4>\n<p>Disable it!</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-viml\">\n      <div class=\"code-bar\">\n      <span class=\"mdi mdi-content-copy\"></span>\n      <span class=\"code-lang\">viml</span>\n      </div><pre><code><span class=\"pl-k\">let</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\"><span class=\"pl-k\">g:</span>airline</span>#extensions#<span class=\"pl-c1\">wordcount</span>#enabled <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">0</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508170-1b39b280-b626-11ea-8074-b72877697249.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508170-1b39b280-b626-11ea-8074-b72877697249.jpg\" alt=\"6\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h4>\n      <a id=\"article-fancy-style\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#fancy-style\">\n      #</a> Fancy style?</h4>\n<p>Yes Badwolf!</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-viml\">\n      <div class=\"code-bar\">\n      <span class=\"mdi mdi-content-copy\"></span>\n      <span class=\"code-lang\">viml</span>\n      </div><pre><code><span class=\"pl-k\">let</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\"><span class=\"pl-k\">g:</span>airline_theme</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>badwolf<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508176-1d9c0c80-b626-11ea-90fe-8f8ed9716ff3.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508176-1d9c0c80-b626-11ea-90fe-8f8ed9716ff3.jpg\" alt=\"7\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a><br>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508179-1ecd3980-b626-11ea-9fde-581b255c956b.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508179-1ecd3980-b626-11ea-9fde-581b255c956b.jpg\" alt=\"8\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h4>\n      <a id=\"article-do-not-want-extra-gt-s\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#do-not-want-extra-gt-s\">\n      #</a> Do not want extra <code>&gt;</code> s?</h4>\n<p>Disable it!</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-viml\">\n      <div class=\"code-bar\">\n      <span class=\"mdi mdi-content-copy\"></span>\n      <span class=\"code-lang\">viml</span>\n      </div><pre><code><span class=\"pl-k\">let</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\"><span class=\"pl-k\">g:</span>airline_skip_empty_sections</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">1</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508184-2260c080-b626-11ea-9190-e9430a4a6b8c.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/85508184-2260c080-b626-11ea-9190-e9430a4a6b8c.jpg\" alt=\"9\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>","createdAt":"2019-02-09T00:00:00.000Z","lastEditedAt":"2021-02-22T01:59:03.000Z","image":"/blog/img/5a6f75bf.png","imageLazy":"ACAAkDASIAAhEBAxEB/8QAFQABAQ$AAP/xAAZEAEAAgM$RFDUYH/xAAUAQE$AAB/8QAFREBAQ$AAH/2gAMAwEAAhEDEQA/AJZur3OwFL//2Q==","serializedHeadings":"[{\"level\":2,\"slug\":\"trouble-shooting\",\"content\":\"Trouble Shooting\"},{\"level\":4,\"slug\":\"only-mode-and-filename-is-displayed\",\"content\":\"Only mode and filename is displayed!\"},{\"level\":4,\"slug\":\"no-fancy-gt-s-there\",\"content\":\"No fancy <code>&gt;</code> s there!\"},{\"level\":4,\"slug\":\"there-are-dots-following-the-mode\",\"content\":\"There are dots following the mode!\"},{\"level\":4,\"slug\":\"i-do-not-need-the-section-z-so-long\",\"content\":\"I do not need the section Z so long!\"},{\"level\":4,\"slug\":\"what-if-i-need-a-tab-bar\",\"content\":\"What if I need a tab bar?\"},{\"level\":4,\"slug\":\"the-word-count-is-annoying\",\"content\":\"The word count is annoying!\"},{\"level\":4,\"slug\":\"fancy-style\",\"content\":\"Fancy style?\"},{\"level\":4,\"slug\":\"do-not-want-extra-gt-s\",\"content\":\"Do not want extra <code>&gt;</code> s?\"}]","labels":[{"id":"blog: programming","type":"blog","name":"programming","color":"60b3bc","path":"/blog/programming/"},{"id":"tag: vim","type":"tag","name":"vim","color":"007f00","path":"/tag/vim/"}],"reactions":[],"comments":[]}},"context":{}}